{"tid":225604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川普：願見金正恩，我絕對很榮幸這樣做","createTime":"2017-05-02T01:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T03:30:40.000Z","uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"82f50df45669ce29a74819b18e67964b5100fb26","tid":225604,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:46:59.000Z","msg":"美國總統川普表示，在適當的情況下，願意見北韓領導人金正恩，「如果和他會面是適當的，我絕對很榮幸這樣做。」<br />\n<br />\n川普在近日播出的哥倫比亞廣播公司（CBS）的「面對國家」（Face The Nation）專訪中，稱讚金正恩是一名「很聰明的人」（pretty smart cookie）。<br />\n<br />\n對於美國和北韓是否會發生軍事衝突，川普表示，「<span style=\"color: red;\">我認為不應該對外公布我方所有的行動，就如同下棋一樣，我不會讓人知道我的想法，</span>我只想說，金正恩最終會有更好的飛彈，不過，我們不會容許這件事發生。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />侵仔"},{"pid":"a276d2f9823b20aacf9fe7790bfe43c0f5d50766","tid":225604,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:52:01.000Z","msg":"侵棋王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"145fd08a71ae67c41fc90d14c1292ce5f5988861","tid":225604,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:59:53.000Z","msg":"棋王2017<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a84637470185dd95daa022ff9b116e80bbe070f5","tid":225604,"uid":50616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T02:01:24.000Z","msg":"生意佬真的係生意佬"},{"pid":"3ff604f4461ab93960317e44b6334efb96157a2a","tid":225604,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T02:02:13.000Z","msg":"去北韓見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6771da7cf6ef9e1a1c02b60c3a7613b91a4b817","tid":225604,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T02:09:28.000Z","msg":"又多個棋王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9204a27a4e312